---
title: Pan-Seared Pork with Onion Gravy, Broccolini and Rosemary Mashed Potatoes
description: We’ve infused a delicious gravy with sweet red onion and fragrant rosemary. Creamy mashed potatoes soak up all that
goodness. This is comfort food at its finest!
